#### Latihan 2A.2: Button dengan Debouncing

Buatlah program yang:
- Menggunakan 1 tombol (pin 2)
- Toggle LED (pin 13) setiap kali tombol ditekan
- Implementasi debouncing untuk mencegah multiple trigger
- Tampilkan state LED di Serial Monitor

**Kode Template:**
```cpp
const int BUTTON_PIN = 2;
const int LED_PIN = 13;

bool ledState = false;
bool lastButtonState = HIGH;
unsigned long lastDebounceTime = 0;
const unsigned long debounceDelay = 50;

void setup() {
  Serial.begin(9600);
  pinMode(LED_PIN, OUTPUT);
  pinMode(BUTTON_PIN, INPUT_PULLUP);
}

void loop() {
  // TODO: Implementasi debouncing dan toggle logic
}
```

**Deliverable:** Screenshot Serial Monitor menunjukkan LED state changes.

