### Track C - Game Development

#### Latihan 2C.1: Movable Character

Buatlah program SFML dengan character yang dapat digerakkan:

**Requirements:**
- Window 800x600 pixels
- Character (bisa circle atau rectangle) yang dapat digerakkan dengan WASD
- Character tidak boleh keluar dari window boundaries
- Movement smooth dengan delta time
- Display position di window title atau text

**Kode Template:**
```cpp
#include <SFML/Graphics.hpp>
#include <sstream>

int main() {
    sf::RenderWindow window(sf::VideoMode(800, 600), "Moving Character");
    
    // Character
    sf::CircleShape player(30);
    player.setFillColor(sf::Color::Green);
    player.setPosition(400, 300);
    
    float speed = 200.0f;
    sf::Clock clock;
    
    while (window.isOpen()) {
        float dt = clock.restart().asSeconds();
        
        // TODO: Event handling
        
        // TODO: Movement with boundary checking
        
        // TODO: Update window title with position
        
        // Render
        window.clear(sf::Color::White);
        window.draw(player);
        window.display();
    }
    
    return 0;
}
```

**Deliverable:** Screenshot program running dengan character di berbagai positions.

