#### Latihan 2D.2: Platform-Specific Code

Buatlah program cross-platform yang:
- Display current platform (Windows, Linux, atau macOS)
- Get current working directory (platform-specific implementation)
- Sleep function yang work di semua platform

**Kode Template:**
```cpp
#include <iostream>
#include <string>

#ifdef _WIN32
    #include <windows.h>
    #include <direct.h>
    #define getcwd _getcwd
    const std::string PLATFORM = "Windows";
#elif __linux__
    #include <unistd.h>
    const std::string PLATFORM = "Linux";
#elif __APPLE__
    #include <unistd.h>
    const std::string PLATFORM = "macOS";
#endif

void sleep_ms(int milliseconds) {
    // TODO: Platform-specific implementation
}

std::string getCurrentDirectory() {
    // TODO: Get current working directory
    return "";
}

int main() {
    std::cout << "Platform: " << PLATFORM << "\n";
    std::cout << "Current Directory: " << getCurrentDirectory() << "\n";
    
    std::cout << "Sleeping 2 seconds...\n";
    sleep_ms(2000);
    std::cout << "Done!\n";
    
    return 0;
}
```

**Deliverable:** Screenshot output di platform yang tersedia.

